---
---
<section class="bg-white py-14 md:py-20 px-5 border-t border-gray-100">
  <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto">

    <p class="text-center text-[11px] md:text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] mb-10" style="color: #e8590c;">
      Quem vai te guiar
    </p>

    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-[260px_1fr] gap-10 md:gap-14 items-start">

      {/* ── FOTO ── */}
      <div class="flex justify-center md:justify-start">
        <div class="w-56 md:w-full aspect-[3/4] rounded-2xl overflow-hidden border-4 border-white shadow-xl bg-gray-100 flex items-center justify-center">
          <img
            src="/images/seminario/guaciara-foto.webp"
            alt="Guaciara Fornaciari"
            class="w-full h-full object-cover"
            width="320"
            height="426"
          />
        </div>
      </div>

      {/* ── CONTEÚDO ── */}
      <div>
        <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-1">Guaciara Fornaciari</h2>
        <p class="text-sm mb-6" style="color: #e8590c; font-weight: 500;">
          Fonoaudióloga · Professora · Ex-coordenadora pedagógica
        </p>

        <p class="text-sm md:text-base text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-3">
          Criadora da Fábrica Mágica, plataforma que hoje atende mais de
          <strong class="text-gray-900">4.747 professoras</strong> em todo o Brasil. Mais de 19 anos de experiência
          na Educação Infantil.
        </p>
        <p class="text-sm md:text-base text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-8">
          Neste Seminário compartilha o método que usa há quase duas décadas
          para escrever relatórios técnicos, dentro da BNCC, com clareza —
          mesmo nas situações mais delicadas.
        </p>

        {/* Números */}
        <div class="grid grid-cols-3 gap-3 mb-8">
          <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-2xl p-4 text-center border border-gray-100">
            <p class="text-2xl font-bold mb-1" style="color: #2C3E99;">4.747</p>
            <p class="text-xs text-gray-500 leading-tight">Professoras impactadas</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-2xl p-4 text-center border border-gray-100">
            <p class="text-2xl font-bold mb-1" style="color: #2C3E99;">19 anos</p>
            <p class="text-xs text-gray-500 leading-tight">de experiência</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-2xl p-4 text-center border border-gray-100">
            <p class="text-2xl font-bold mb-1" style="color: #2C3E99;">+500</p>
            <p class="text-xs text-gray-500 leading-tight">aulas realizadas</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        {/* Selos */}
        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2 bg-gray-50 border border-gray-200 rounded-full px-4 py-1.5">
            <span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full flex-shrink-0" style="background-color: #e8590c;"></span>
            <span class="text-xs text-gray-600">Fonoaudióloga</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2 bg-gray-50 border border-gray-200 rounded-full px-4 py-1.5">
            <span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full flex-shrink-0" style="background-color: #e8590c;"></span>
            <span class="text-xs text-gray-600">Professora</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2 bg-gray-50 border border-gray-200 rounded-full px-4 py-1.5">
            <span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full flex-shrink-0" style="background-color: #e8590c;"></span>
            <span class="text-xs text-gray-600">Ex-coordenadora pedagógica</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2 bg-gray-50 border border-gray-200 rounded-full px-4 py-1.5">
            <span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full flex-shrink-0" style="background-color: #e8590c;"></span>
            <span class="text-xs text-gray-600">Fundadora Fábrica Mágica</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2 bg-gray-50 border border-gray-200 rounded-full px-4 py-1.5">
            <span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full flex-shrink-0" style="background-color: #e8590c;"></span>
            <span class="text-xs text-gray-600">Especialista em Educação Infantil</span>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
